  <title>libz-&libz-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      libz is a general purpose data compression library. The data format used
      by libz is described by RFC 1950 (zlib format), RFC 1951 (deflate
      format), and RFC 1952 (gzip format).
    </para>

